	<title>About APC - American Power Conversion</title>
	<meta name="description" content="American Power Conversion (APC) is a leading manufacturer of uninterruptible power supplies and surge protection products for personal, professional, and network applications. APC offers far more than basic power protection for a total solution with products featuring  hot swappable user replaceable batteries, power management software, SNMP accessories and data line protection.  Products include Back-UPS, Back-UPS Pro, Back-UPS Pro PNP Bundles, Smart-UPS v/s, Smart-UPS, Matrix UPS, PowerChute Plus software, PowerNet SNMP, ProtectNet, and SurgeArrest.   See our new Rack-Mount Smart-UPS and Back-UPS Pro Plug and Play UPS, Notebook Surge Arrest, NetShelter, and Back-UPS Office.">
